<th>Amount in transaction currency credit</th>
<th>Balance</th>
<th>Currency</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>FTI-10010</td>
<td>Invoice</td>
<td>6/25/2015</td>
<td>10010</td>
<td>1,000.00</td>
<td></td>
<td>1,000.00</td>
<td>USD</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>From the <strong>Customer</strong> or <strong>Customer transactions</strong> page, Arnie can open the <strong>Settle transactions</strong> page to view the dates and amounts of cash discounts that are available for the invoice. The due date is July 25, and a cash discount of 10.00 is available if the invoice is paid by July 9.</p>
